<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8323700>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Rohdea tuberculata. A. Habit. B. Inflorescence in vertical view. C. Young flower in vertical view. D. Blade. E. Inflorescence in lateral view. F. Stigma. G. Old flower in vertical view. H. Outer bract (left) and inner bract (right). I. Old flower without stamens in vertical view. J. Old flower, longitudinal section. K. Young flower in longitudinal section and with pistil. L. Young lower in longitudinal section without pistil. M. Young flower in external view. N & O. Stamen with lobe in young flower (N: vertical view, N: lateral view). Photos by H. Z. Feng." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8323700/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

